Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這種地方幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夢不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現實才更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次免費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把錢包帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  你肯定喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟這扭蛋很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面裝著你想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我並沒有什麼想要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,別騙人了  當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是該冷藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是還活著  是不是應該保溫才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  說不定會把它煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它能打破嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不如說  我可以打破它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把包放下  你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,愛！老師來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶媽媽  不用勉強叫她起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是來送這週的講義的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.69,Top,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.31,Top,,0,0,0,,總是麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.94,Top,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有  不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.44,Top,,0,0,0,,我只是回家路上來看看罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再去那裡看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會在學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不搞大點她不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…  那就再多加點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？你還說是我做得過火呢  你個魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給在學校的各位提問：
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是班上有人被欺凌該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯！正確答案當然是視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,打破蛋  把蛋打破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奇妙蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快點打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這很硬  我打不破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快點打破！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打破！打破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你這不是做得挺好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  為什麼要在這種地方打破啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是完事了  就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要用這種口氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,高高在上讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用普通的語氣不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說我也應聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要跑囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.93,Default,,800,0,0,,那個… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,800,0,,要快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它們就是「視而不見」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是肝臟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是夢  一場噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看你的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的傷口不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說這是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但對我來說這是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,總之  在打鈴之前我們要一直跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它們只追我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了你在這個世界是不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你的眼睛和心臟沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那還叫不死身嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭  為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你買了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,說是第一個免費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  沒什麼比免費更貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你沒有朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是沒有  是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就不會打破蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不過表面朋友也是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,「是啊是啊」「我知道」「好可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只會這樣附和的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我沒有摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在回想起來  摯友真的很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友會分手  但摯友是一輩子的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有過男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我先問的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們「一二」一起說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,錯的是它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  它們不來追我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不來追我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫長瀨小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那長瀨同學就坐大戶同學的旁邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起回家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,「欸」是什麼反應啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太傷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡這麼清靜  是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是醜女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛又大又圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的髮型？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要遮住這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的傘呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,愛  你朋友來找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我朋友  我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你忘記的東西送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,雙眼虹膜顏色不一樣  這叫做異色瞳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在貓和狗之中比較常見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得沒必要藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我因此受欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做摯友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不行…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能做摯友  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我辜負了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我交到的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一點  就差一點就要打鈴了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,斑馬線  即使和人群一起過也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再視而不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經怒不可遏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫西城胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,愛… 該告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘記我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,得救的就只有你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想把摯友找回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有點溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我保護了胡桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  要是我保護更多的人  小糸就能復活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,愛  來吃飯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天氣特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要總是睡在床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我把洗的衣服晾起來了  下午幫忙收回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.09,Top,,0,0,0,,呀  都已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  我在那邊是不死身  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽今天早上要開會  所以現在就得出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是晚上溜出去在外面被捲入什麼事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  傷情怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,錢包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要保護多少人小糸才能復活？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,唯獨這件事  我沒辦法告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果同時保護多個人  那就會更快一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是個貪婪的小笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒保護好  你也沒辦法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  敵人也不全是那麼容易對付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟它們只是「視而不見」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一群烏合之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的摯友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在某個世界裡變成了雕像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,除非她的朋友去到那個世界  不然她就永遠那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃她也自殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是大號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你左邊的是小號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有別的客人先來了  你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  還有其他人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也一直很擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,身材好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,待續
